\v 7 K…®ni tukm…ô ror yermam…ô k…®rik tukr…®ni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô yakeiku…ô, k…®ni kafak norien kape neiku…ôyen ramor …ôpu m…ô Kughen p…®s…®n …ôm…ô ram…ôfrak…®s, k…®ni narmam…ô tukhani vi vi In, meinai kharkun m…ô In p…®s…®n …ôm…ô ratuatuk, k…®ni tukm…ô kafak norien kape neiku…ôyen ramor swatuk m…ô narmam…ô tukhav…ôh-si hakt…ô Kughen, r…®p…ôh natuatukien m…ô Kughen tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ô narp…®nien k…®mi yo.‚Äù
