\v 14 ?M…ôr…®g tukm…ô narmam…ô khap…ôh n…®shat…ôt…ôyen ye Kughen Yermaru, tukshawor p…ôn iran m…®ne m…®sokr…ôn k…®n In m…ô tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôri…ô? ?K…®ni tukm…ô khap…ôh n…®s…ôr…®gien n…ôvsaoyen k…®n, tukshawor p…ôn iran m…®ne m…®shat…ôt…ô iran? ?K…®ni tukm…ô yermam…ô k…®rik r…®k…ôk tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen tuk …ôri…ô, tukshawor p…ôn iran m…®ne m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôvsaoyen k…®n?
