\v 1 P…ôh yakaiyoh tuk n…ôgkiarien k…®rik ye n…®kar…®n kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. ?In e n…ôfrak…®sien m…ô Kughen r…®mukreik…®n-p…ô n…®meitaan k…®mi kafan narmam…ô u…ô n…®kam? N…®kam. Taks…ôm-ru yo. In r…®m…®p…ôh nukreik…®n-p…ôyen n…®meitaan k…®mi yo e yem…ô Isrel k…®rik, kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Ebraham, n…®t…ô kape Benjamin.\x - \xo 11:1 \xt 1 Saml 12:22; Sam 94:14; Fil 3:5 \x*
